    "tags": []
   },
   "source": [
    "# ML from DFT data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- learn form library features\n",
    "- learn from bop features\n",
    "- combination of features\n",
    "- compare different regression methods\n",
    "- compare different test-train splittings\n",
    "- Learn on increasing domain knowledge"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    " - input: clean features dataframes from pickles\n",
    " - output : plots and Models"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {
    "slideshow": {
     "slide_type": "skip"
    },
    "tags": []
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from Tools.DatasetTools.Commoms import *"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Parameters "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "slideshow": {
     "slide_type": "subslide"
    },
    "tags": []
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "dataset = 'Fe-Mo'#'Cr-Co-W'#\n",
    "system = dataset.replace('-','')\n",
    "CASE = 'INITIAL'  #, 'INITIAL', RELAXED\n",
    "# MODEL = 'ORTHOGONALOS' #, 'ORTHOGONAL', 'CANONICAL','ORTOGONALOS'"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Targets"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "BS = load_fully_curated_briefsummary(dataset)"
